nodes.text: A male Human member of House Alde, a noble house of the planet Alderaan, held the title of earl sometime before the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. Considered to be undistinguished by other nobles, the earl was arranged to be married to Gesselle of House House Organa on Gesselle's eighteenth birthday, but the wedding was postponed and ultimately cancelled for reasons unknown to the general public.
The Alde earl was first mentioned in Gesselle Organa's Codex entry in the 2011 video game Star Wars: The Old Republic.
